title: MusicNews | Watch: This video of Drake dancing to The Rugrats theme is mesmerising
text:
It's both strangely cool nd a little bit creepy.
We bet the theme is embedded into your brain now. Apple had previously released the official video today. But we thought this was much better.
Try looking at Drake in the same way, we just dare you.
